=Bio=

Jorge Luis Zapico

"I’m a PhD researcher at KTH (Stockholm Royal Institute of Technology), working in the Centre of Sustainable Communications (CESC) and under the department of Media Technology and Industrial Ecology.

My research area is the intersection of media technology (mainly internet) and sustainability (mainly climate change), focusing on a hands-on approach of using new technology to help the transition towards a low-carbon lifestyle.

I’m the project coordinator for Data Driven Sustainability."
(http://www.sustainableinternet.org/author/)

